      "description": "We are pleased to offer this peerless example of automotive engineering, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior environment that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously curated and mechanically beyond reproach, this specimen represents the definitive choice for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
